  "description": "The Fibonacci torus knot (5,8) approximates the golden ratio — P/Q approaches φ as you climb the Fibonacci sequence. The pqScale at (5,8) is 0.962, producing coupling asymmetry that never fully resolves into a periodic beat pattern. macroKnot=0.35 blends partial Solomon ring architecture into the Torus surface geometry — the golden winding encounters two-ring resistance. LFO1 on braid depth at 0.025 Hz (40-second cycle) breathes the topology slowly. LFO2 on filter at 0.06 Hz wanders the spectral landscape. Two incommensurate modulations with a combined period of approximately 2.5 minutes.",
